high_descs: Walk towards the fridge, then turn right and walk to the window, then turn left to the grey counter.
Pick up the rightmost green apple on the counter.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right toward the stove and open the microwave door above the stove.
Place the apple inside the microwave to the left of the mug, close the microwave door, and start the microwave, wait, then open the microwave door and take the apple out.
Turn left to face the sink, then turn right towards the wall and walk forward, then turn right towards the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the apple inside in front of the lettuce, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk forward to the fridge then turn right and walk until you hit a wall then turn left to face a coffee pot.
Pick up the green apple to the left of the coffee pot.
Turn left and position yourself in front of the stove.
Cook the apple in the microwave and take it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the front of the fridge so you are facing it.
Place the apple on the middle of the middle shelf towards the front.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Walk straight, turn right near the fridge, walk straight towards the wall and turn left to face the counter top.
Pick up the green apple next to the stove.
Walk slightly to the left to the stove and look up to the microwave on top of the stove.
Open the microwave, heat it up for a few seconds, pick it up again from the microwave and close the microwave.
Walk to the left to go to the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge between the lettuce and the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated green apple in the fridge between the lettuce and the potato.

high_descs: Walk straight towards the fridge then turn right head to the coffee maker on your left
Pick up the apple on the left side of the coffee maker
Turn to your left then walk straight face the microwave on your right
Open the microwave warm the apple then get it again close the microwave
Turn to your left walk straight head to the fridge
Open the fridge and put in the apple then close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put the heated apple in the fridge

high_descs: Walk towards the fridge, turn right towards the window, turn left to face the coffee maker.
Pick up the left green apple on the counter.
Turn left, walk to the middle of the stove, and then turn right to face it.
Place the apple inside the microwave directly above the stove to heat it, and take the apple out.
Turn left, walk towards the fridge, and turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the apple in front of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Go forward to the fridge then turn right, then go forward and turn left at the counter with the coffee maker.
Pick up the apple on the counter, to the left of the coffee maker.
Turn left, go straight, then turn right and look up to face the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Go to the fridge, to your left.
Put the apple in the fridge, to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the fridge.
